main event: A woman in Greenfield, Wisconsin reported seeing a round, orange-red object with a dome and glow that was stationary at first, then descended in a swaying motion.
interesting points: The object was the size of a meat platter and had a dome and glow.
The object descended briskly from ground level while swaying.
The sighting lasted 5-7 minutes, from midnight to 12:07 AM.
The weather conditions were perfectly clear with unlimited visibility.
No physical evidence or photographs were provided.
sighted object: a round, orange-red object with a dome and glow
